# Trinidad Sour

+TPC +Cocktails +Recipe +ClassicCocktails

* Glass - *Coup*
* Ice - *None*
* Method - *Reverse dry-shake & fine-strain*
* Angosturra Bitters - *25ml*
* JD Rye - *10ml*
* ODK Lemon Juice - *25ml*
* Giffard Orgeat Syrup - *20ml*
* Egg White - *1*
* Garnish - *Bitters swirl*

